/**
 * Phase 1 Parsing Test: Basic Arithmetic Expressions
 * Tests basic arithmetic operations and operator precedence
 * @phase 1
 * @complexity basic
 * @component parsing
 */

// Basic arithmetic operations
1 + 2
3 - 4
5 * 6
7 / 8
10 % 3

// Operator precedence tests
2 + 3 * 4       // Should parse as 2 + (3 * 4)
(2 + 3) * 4     // Should parse as (2 + 3) * 4
10 - 5 + 2      // Should parse as (10 - 5) + 2
8 / 2 * 2       // Should parse as (8 / 2) * 2

// Mixed operations
(1 + 2) * (3 + 4)
10 / (2 + 3)
5 * 4 + 3 * 2